se novel techniques, a\nconsistent and conservative scheme for the present multiphase flow model is\ndeveloped and analyzed. Numerical applications demonstrate that the present\nmodel and scheme are robust and effective in studying complicated multiphase\ndynamics, especially for those with large-density ratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2020 16:56:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2020 22:45:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 02:48:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 20:03:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
